.TH LEDD 8 "@HIDLOOM_VERSION@" "HIDloom" "System Administration"
.SH NAME
ledd \- LED animation and direct-frame daemon
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B python3 -m ledd.ledd
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B ledd
controls the LED strip, receives semantic key events from logicd, applies
VialRGB effects, and accepts direct-frame producer input.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B -h, --help
Show command help.
.SH ENVIRONMENT
Common variables include \fBLEDD_DIRECT_FRAME_SOCK\fR,
\fBLEDD_DIRECT_FRAME_STATUS\fR, \fBLEDD_DIRECT_FRAME_FALLBACK\fR, and
\fBLEDD_I2CD_SOCKET\fR.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR hidloom-ledd (5),
.BR logicd (8),
.BR ledd-shutdown (8)
.br
Lighting documentation:
https://github.com/cqa02303/hidloom/tree/@HIDLOOM_GIT_SHA@/docs/lighting
